data.description: THIS IS THE ONE! Welcome to this 3 bedroom, SPACIOUS  BRICK RANCH situated on a LARGE, nicely LANDSCAPED parcel, located minutes from DOWNTOWN ROCHESTER, SHOPPING, and TRAILS. This wonderful home boasts a NEWLY RENOVATED BATH featuring NEW TILE, TUB, VANITY, and HARDWARE. NEW LUXURY PLANK FLOORING IN KITCHEN, LAUNDRY ROOM, POWDER ROOM, and 3-SEASON ROOM and RECENTLY DRYWALLED (removed dated paneling) FAMILY ROOM along with LVP flooring round out some of the updates completed on this home. FINISHED BASEMENT offers additional ENTERTAINING/OFFICE SPACE and STORAGE. This property is a GREAT VALUE and SHOULD NOT BE MISSED!
